{"_id":"03abf95b-15bb-4885-bf84-0078166877dc","type":"skill","name":"Medicine","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill_id":"medicine","domain":"Technology and Sciences","rank":1,"stat":"intelligence","description":"The medicine skill is used to diagnose, understand, and treat medical conditions such as injuries, diseases, or poisons. When you Rest, you may forego your own rest to either Help an ally on their check with the Medicine skill or allow them to make an Strength check to cure themselves of a poison, Helped by your medicine check."}}
{"_id":"04b3859d-12f1-4f36-9700-d7c391621083","type":"ability","name":"Long-Term Care","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Long-Term Care","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"Allies that have been in your presence more than 24 hours have their Critical wound threshold increased by 5 and have a Boon to their healing rolls when resting. Whenever an ally in your area accepts stat burn to take an Epic Boon, roll a d4. On a 4, they do not take the burn.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"0c05f65a-0f6f-4a18-979b-0f39554935ce","type":"ability","name":"Improved First Aid","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Improved First Aid","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"During a rest, when using First Aid, if you do not heal any of your own wounds or burn you may burn Intelligence or Intuition instead of Endurance. You gain a Boon to any checks made to use First Aid.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"157f172b-d4ed-48c2-a1ee-9d7396383c10","type":"ability","name":"Forensics","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Forensics","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"By spending 10 minutes carefully examining a dead creature or other remains, you can a lot of information about the creature. In addition to the approximate time and manner of death, you gain any information that would be gained by an Investigation check. You may also ask the GM one specific question about the creature, and get a general answer.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"2e1dd0db-3373-4b76-a16b-ea8934ab2aa2","type":"ability","name":"Pharmacology","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Pharmacology","rank":"1","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You can create drugs as though through the Alchemy skill, and can carry crafted items or Alchemy supplies as calculated by your Medicine or Alchemy ranks, whichever is higher.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"3365b6c3-34ab-4ff4-be7e-88e6157b2995","type":"ability","name":"Second Opinion","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Second Opinion","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"3","description":"You may use this upon failing a Medicine check to reroll. You gain an Epic Boon on the check.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"4221770a-4697-48e0-a6c4-501a908e3cc7","type":"ability","name":"Diagnosis","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Diagnosis","rank":"3","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"strength","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"Can be used against any living creature. On a success, you learn the target's damage thresholds, Vulnerabilities, ongoing conditions, and number of Minor Wounds and Major Wounds. If used on an ally, you gain a boon to any checks made to cure conditions from which they suffer (such as poison), and there is no need for them to defend.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"6c4ff6bc-ff6b-435c-b823-bd7bef6d3db7","type":"ability","name":"Do Some Harm","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Do Some Harm","rank":"5","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You may use this ability immediately after hitting with a weapon attack. You inflict a Minor Wound, even if your original attack did not.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"72861dbd-d961-4ca3-bcea-57936393b7e2","type":"ability","name":"Bedside Manner","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Bedside Manner","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"Can only be used when the Venture Modifier is positive. When catching your breath or taking a rest, you may make make a Medicine check against the Venture difficulty to attempt to calm and refresh your allies. On a success, remove a consequence from the tracker.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"83174a02-70f2-4d86-ab1b-f285c5ced404","type":"ability","name":"Anatomist","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Anatomist","rank":"1","type":"technique","action":"fast","defense":"strength","target":"Single","range":"Short","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You attempt to identify a weakness of a humanoid creature. On a success, it is vulnerable to all your attacks until the end of the combat.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"8fa179da-6df6-4d77-86d5-aab22307f6cd","type":"ability","name":"Professional Opinion","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Professional Opinion","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"2","description":"You can speak from a place of authority in matters related to medicine. You may substitute your Medicine skill in the place of Influence or Investigation when trying to bluff a diagnosis, convince someone to let you provide medical care, or in other situations where medical knowledge or authority may sway someone (such as speaking with a medical professional).","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"e7a9a31b-9c4c-480b-a67a-a7c54c173cbb","type":"ability","name":"Triage","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Triage","rank":"5","type":"technique","action":"slow","defense":"","target":"","range":"Adjacent","duration":"","cost":"1","description":"You may use this after an ally becomes Critically Wounded. They heal one wound and one stat burn, and are able to move or flee, but are unable to take other actions. An ally cannot benefit from this more than once in a Venture.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"vim","skill_id":"medicine"}}
{"_id":"e805e115-3b86-4460-9e7b-a316a891f373","type":"ability","name":"Do No Harm","img":"systems/venture-rpg/assets/skills/medicine.svg","system":{"skill":"Medicine","name":"Do No Harm","rank":"3","type":"ability","action":"","defense":"","target":"","range":"","duration":"","cost":"","description":"When you use First Aid during a rest, for each ally you assist roll a d4. On a 4, the ally does not burn stats.","domain":"Technology and Sciences","costtype":"","skill_id":"medicine"}}
